org.jfree.data

Class TimeSeriesTableModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
      • org.jfree.data.TimeSeriesTableModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.util.EventListener, javax.swing.table.TableModel, SeriesChangeListener

    public class TimeSeriesTableModel
extends javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
implements SeriesChangeListener
    Wrapper around a time series to convert it to a table model for use in a JTable.
